channel.title: Someone Help With the Nulls!
channel.description:
I've got an issue with my server. Someone nulled it and every time I put the server online, 200 nulls come on and crash the server every time and people can't log in. Here's a picture of the runserver when I open it and the nulls logging in:
[url=http://[img]http://www.imgjoe.com/x/nulls.png[/img]][img]http://www.imgjoe.com/x/nulls.png[/img][/url]
And my server is a 317. Can someone help me get rid of these stupid nulls? :confused: :confused:
